---[ License ]---

Read doc/license.htm

---[ How to install ]---

Just run ./secondlife.  

---[ How to fuck with Lua ]---

Macros are in lua/Macros.  They can be executed from the chatbar in the form of 

	/m FileNameWithoutTheExtension (Arguments as required.)

Hooks are the plugins the make use of automatically-fired events fired by the viewer's lua engine.
You can find a list of these events in lua/EventHandling.lua.


